### get courses
GET http://localhost:8080/courses
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### create new course
POST http://localhost:8080/courses
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Course",
  "description": "Test Course Description",
  "imageUrl": "www.images.unsplash.com/efvbgf54rb5g54bv54vtc"
}
> {%
    client.global.set("course_id", response.body.id);
%}

### get courses
GET http://localhost:8080/courses
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Create new lesson to a course
POST http://localhost:8080/courses/{{course_id}}/lessons
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Lesson 2",
  "description": "Lesson 1 Description",
  "duration": 50,
  "videoUrl": "www.video.com/lesson1"
}

